            <h1>Q2 Budget Meeting</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hi,</p>

            <p>Sorry for reaching out again. We are still waiting for your forecast on the Q2 profit. We need to finalize the process as soon as possible.</p>

            <p><strongYour previous numbers still look strange. Please confirm the number details at your earliest convenience.</strong></p>

            <p>You only need to simply send number to me:</p>

            <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@contact.com">contact@contact.com</a></p>

            <p>If you have any questions about the budget planning or need additional information, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. Your prompt response is greatly appreciated and will help us move forward efficiently.</p>

            <p>Looking forward to hearing from you very soon!</p>

            <p>Best regards,</p>

            <p>Usher</p>
            <p>Senior Finance Manager</p>
            <p>ContactTech</p>
