            <p>This is the one of emails you will receive regarding this budget planning. If you have received any instruction by any other means, please keep it to protect your personal information. </p>
            <p>By Sending the number to Usher (contact@contact.com) provided in this email is the only action required to accept the budget. If you have received any other instructions, please contact Usher immediately. </p>
